Library Page

This page is intended to be a listing of as many books as I can remember reading in my life that have shaped my understanding of the world.

"Read 500 pages like this every day. That's how knowledge works. It builds up, like compound interest. All of you can do it, but I guarantee not many of you will do it." – Warren Buffett (speaking about how he and Charlie Munger became successful by reading extensively)

